## Frontend environment variables (Vite)
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - Variables must start with VITE_
# - These values are read at BUILD TIME (not runtime) for Vite static builds.
#
# If your frontend and backend are deployed on different domains, you MUST set
# VITE_API_BASE_URL to your backend service URL so other devices can reach it.

# Example (Render / Railway / Fly / etc):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-backend-service.example.com

